    "title": "Industrial Floor Coatings for Animal Wellness - Elite Crete Systems",
    "content": "Animal Wellness\nOur flooring systems for the animal wellness industry are durable, abrasion resistant coatings. These antimicrobial surfaces are also chemical and stain resistant against common cleaners as well as biological animal waste.\nAdvantages\nSeamless, non-permeable and antimicrobial surfaces\nScratch resistant, withstands animal claws and teeth\nIntegrated cove base and vertical applications available for wall protection\nChemical and thermal shock resistant for areas subject to steam cleaning\nResistant to animal waste, including medicated urine\nHighly chemical resistant, optional \u2018novolac coatings\u2019\nCoefficient of friction (COF) meets and exceeds ADA Flat & Inclined Surfaces, OSHA and NFPA requirements\nVeterinary offices\nWaiting room and lobbies\nExam rooms\nKennels & daycares\nGrooming areas\nLaboratory facilities\nLivestock areas\nSterilization room\nX-ray and MRI facilities\nRestrooms and breakrooms\nMechanical closet\nUrethane Cement\nREFLECTOR\nEnhancer\nREFLECTOR\nEnhancer HD",
